videos.description: Frank Booker sinks a 3-pointer after Chris Silva grabs the offensive rebound.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Booker drills 3 on second chance

videos.description: Chuma Okeke sinks a 3 off a behind-the-back, no-look pass from Jared Harper that hypes up the Auburn crowd.
videos.headline: Harper's sweet behind-the-back dish sets up 3-pointer

videos.description: Frank Booker gets the friendly roll on a deep 3-pointer just before halftime to give the Gamecocks a 37-35 lead.
videos.headline: Booker rattles in 3 to give South Carolina halftime lead

videos.description: Bruce Pearl says Auburn needs to stay poised and keep South Carolina off the boards in the second half.
videos.headline: Pearl: We need more poise in second half

videos.description: The No. 14 Tigers have a big second half and defeat the Gamecocks 79-70, clinching at least a share of their first regular-season title since 1999.
videos.headline: Auburn tops South Carolina, clinches share of SEC title
